	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I don't have enough experience in HoT, but I'd still advise not using Remedy too often, even on casters. In HoT, I'd assume PC casters would have at least 2.5k HPs. Remedy heals for roughly 450HPs? that's less than 1 bubble of health. No point healing for that much. Get a mage to summon haste items for casters  <img src="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif" border="0" alt=""> very useful items.<br />
