	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Another thing that I use remedy for in HoT is the long distance heal to save the puller if he is about to die on his way back in with a mob.  Sometimes they will get stunned and smacked about pretty hard and that 450HP is just enough to keep him alive long enough for the call of hero to snatch him up to safety or for the MT to tag the mob.<br />
